title: Pixel 4 Charger
content: The Google Pixel 4 XL comes with a 18W charger.    If I buy a higher output charger, what is the maximum the phone can support?   In other words, if I bought a 25W charger separately, would it charge faster?  What is the highest wattage it can charge at?
category: Battery and Power, Google Pixel 4 XL
